=\nRapidash\'s horn shows it may have been inspired by {{wp|unicorn}}s, but it also displays a lot of resemblance to a regular {{wp|horse}}. Rapidash and its pre-evolved form may also be based on fiery steeds in mythology, such as those of the Greek god {{wp|Helios}}, {{wp|Skinfaxi and Hrímfaxi|Skinfaxi}} of {{wp|Norse mythology}}, and the horses of the {{wp|Ashvins}} in {{wp|Hindu mythology}}.\n\n====Name origin====\nRapidash may be a combination of \'\'rapid\'\' and \'\'dash\'\', referring to the high speed at which it runs. It could also be a combination of \'\'rapid\'\' and \'\'ash\'\' (referencing its Fire type).\n\nGallop is literally \'\'gallop\'\', a form of running for hoofed animals.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=fire|type2=fire\n|ja=ギャロップ \'\'Gallop\'\'|jameaning=From \'\'gallop\'\'\n|fr=Galopa|frmeaning=From {{tt|\'\'galop\'\'|gallop}}\n|es=Rapidash|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Gallopa|demeaning=From \'\'{{tt|Galopp|gallop}}\'\'\n|it=Rapidash|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=날쌩마 \'\'Nalssengma\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|날쌔다 \'\'Nalssaeda\'\'|swift, nimble}} and {{tt|마 \'\'ma\'\'|horse}}. Includes 쌩 \'\'ssaeng\'\', meaning the sound of something fast.\n|zh_yue=烈焰馬 \'\'Lihtyìhmmáh\'\'|zh_yuemeaning=Means "Raging flame horse" or "Horse of roaring flames"\n|zh_cmn=烈焰馬 / 烈焰马 \'\'Lièyànmǎ\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=Means "Raging flame horse" or "Horse of roaring flames"\n|hi=रेपीदाश \'\'Rapidash\'\'|himeaning=Transcription of English name\n|ru=Рапидаш \'\'Rapidash\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n{{left clear}}\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Platinum\'s Rapidash]]\n\n==External links==\n* {{wp|Ponyta and Rapidash|Article on Wikipedia}}\n\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Fire}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Fire|prevnum=077|prev=Ponyta|nextnum=079|next=Slowpoke}}\n|}\n{{-}}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[Category:Shadow Pokémon in Pokémon XD]]\n\n[[de:Gallopa]]\n[[es:Rapidash]]\n[[fr:Galopa]]\n[[it:Rapidash]]\n[[ja:ギャロップ]]\n[[zh: